WEBVTT

00:07:59.760 --> 00:08:02.536
One of its Latin roots
means "from the earth."

00:08:02.560 --> 00:08:03.800
It's about being grounded.

00:08:04.440 --> 00:08:07.616
So humility doesn't require you
to only do the grunt work.

00:08:07.640 --> 00:08:10.840
It's about realizing you're not
above doing whatever the team needs.

00:08:11.680 --> 00:08:14.216
Think about someone
whose humility you've admired:

00:08:14.240 --> 00:08:17.096
a teammate, a leader, a role model.

00:08:17.120 --> 00:08:18.320
How do they show it?

00:08:19.000 --> 00:08:22.776
We know from research that humility
is revealed through three key actions

00:08:22.800 --> 00:08:24.600
and you can see all of them in Shane.

00:08:25.480 --> 00:08:29.096
One, recognize your own
shortcomings and limitations.

00:08:29.120 --> 00:08:33.496
ML: If Shane did not acknowledge
his own weaknesses and adapt to them,